Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey, who resided on a mango tree, which was on the bank of a river. In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and its wife...
One day, the Crocodile ca,e  to the banks of the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. The next day Crocodile came back for more fruits, as he loved them. As days passed by, the Crocodile and the monkey became good friends...
One day the monkey sent some fruits for the Crocodile's wife. She ate the fruits and liked them.